title: Stop Errything — The 'Cash Me Ousside' Girl Has A Music Video!
text:
OK, Danielle Bregoli , AKA the "Cash Me Ousside" girl , is not singing, thank goodness!
(Though hearing her belt out Adele's "Hello from the ousside" would be pretty hysterical.)
No, the song belongs to rapper Kodak Black , but Danielle's team got special permission to create a music video for Everything 1K .
Related: The #BackPackChallenge Has Resurfaced With A Vengeance 
While it isn't the "official" vid for the song, it has amassed over 4 million views in just 24 hours. So, um... "How bow dah" we guess.
Ch-ch-check out Danielle's ode to the gangsta lifestyle (below)!
